WEBVTT

00:00:29.720 --> 00:00:31.856
with the greatest of their courage,

00:00:31.880 --> 00:00:33.920
wisdom and humility.

00:00:34.680 --> 00:00:36.120
These are my teachers.

00:00:37.160 --> 00:00:38.896
For the last three decades,

00:00:38.920 --> 00:00:42.336
I've been working,
staying and living in India

00:00:42.360 --> 00:00:45.320
and working with women in rural India.

00:00:46.040 --> 00:00:48.160
I was born and brought up in Mumbai.

00:00:49.080 --> 00:00:50.696
When I was in college,

00:00:50.720 --> 00:00:53.936
I met Jayaprakash Narayan,

00:00:53.960 --> 00:00:56.256
famous Gandhian leader

00:00:56.280 --> 00:00:59.400
who inspired youth to work in rural India.